text: Stefan Potocki may refer to: * Stefan Potocki, voivode of Bratslav (1568-1631), governor of Bratslav, starost of Fellin, played a role in the Moldavian Magnate Wars * Stefan Potocki (1624–1648), Polish nobleman, starost of Niżyn * Stefan Aleksander Potocki (1651/1652-1726/1727), Polish nobleman, starost of Belz
